  "content_html": "<div class=\"relative header-and-anchor\"><h4 id=\"h-kkbox-podcast-kkbox\">由 KKBOX 直接經營的 Podcast 錄音室，還有多功能複合式活動空間，感謝 KKBOX 邀請搶先開箱～</h4></div><p>KKBOX 從音樂串流跨足 Podcast，對聽眾和創作者兩端皆端出貼心的服務與功能</p><p>聽眾端：播放器規劃出 Podcast 收聽頁面、主題推薦區塊</p><p>創作者端：實際投資 Firstory 這個本土 Hosting 平台服務商，共同規劃聲音節目孵化輔導系列培訓課程，如今正式成立錄音室品牌 KKBOX STUDIO</p><p>KKBOX STUDIO 規劃了三間錄音室：Mini Box, Small Box, Big Box<br>體驗當天使用的是最大間的 Big Box<br>錄音設施配置都是最多可四人同時錄音和監聽、有獨立 Wifi 可使用<br>主要差別在旁邊陪同者的沙發人數</p><p>讓我印象深刻的是進門後開放式的大廳<br>以中小型創作者來說，做為實體活動場地很好用<br>目測粗估到20人左右都還很夠坐、不擁擠<br>現場提供投影機、投影幕、活動椅以及供訪客飲用的沖泡茶包、瓶裝礦泉水及咖啡機（可以現煮！讓我眼睛一亮，哈哈）<br>想要拍照打卡也有可愛的標語牆和小道具可以用</p><figure float=\"none\" data-type=\"figure\" class=\"img-center\" style=\"max-width: null;\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/papyrus_images/97972eeb505e5d421063449370ac2309.jpg\" blurdataurl=\"data:image/png;base64,\" nextheight=\"1067\" nextwidth=\"800\" class=\"image-node embed\"><figcaption HTMLAttributes=\"[object Object]\" class=\"\">大廳拍照牆</figcaption></figure><figure float=\"none\" data-type=\"figure\" class=\"img-center\" style=\"max-width: null;\"><img src=\"https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0649eb79-ca0c-45b3-9566-59469e5033d0_600x450.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-node embed\"><figcaption HTMLAttributes=\"[object Object]\" class=\"hide-figcaption\"></figcaption></figure><figure float=\"none\" data-type=\"figure\" class=\"img-center\" style=\"max-width: null;\"><img src=\"https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ff5c5b33-b576-4137-85ed-b4b2c967c240_600x450.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-node embed\"><figcaption HTMLAttributes=\"[object Object]\" class=\"hide-figcaption\"></figcaption></figure><figure float=\"none\" data-type=\"figure\" class=\"img-center\" style=\"max-width: null;\"><img src=\"https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/dec90d3d-96ee-44e8-869e-6918ed65f611_400x533.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-node embed\"><figcaption HTMLAttributes=\"[object Object]\" class=\"hide-figcaption\"></figcaption></figure><figure float=\"none\" data-type=\"figure\" class=\"img-center\" style=\"max-width: null;\"><img src=\"https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7cc19d7e-ce84-4442-b235-7368ec421fb6_400x533.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-node embed\"><figcaption HTMLAttributes=\"[object Object]\" class=\"hide-figcaption\"></figcaption></figure><figure float=\"none\" data-type=\"figure\" class=\"img-center\" style=\"max-width: null;\"><img src=\"https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/d9ab482a-7af4-46db-89fd-eef3e03ee683_600x451.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-node embed\"><figcaption HTMLAttributes=\"[object Object]\" class=\"hide-figcaption\"></figcaption></figure><figure float=\"none\" data-type=\"figure\" class=\"img-center\" style=\"max-width: null;\"><img src=\"https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/8e2613fe-4889-4606-8056-0ce977a3448e_400x533.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-node embed\"><figcaption HTMLAttributes=\"[object Object]\" class=\"hide-figcaption\"></figcaption></figure><figure float=\"none\" data-type=\"figure\" class=\"img-center\" style=\"max-width: null;\"><img src=\"https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f0ca469d-c26e-4554-9cfc-0bcb682891c2_800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-node embed\"><figcaption HTMLAttributes=\"[object Object]\" class=\"\">錄音室錄音實況側拍，工作桌椅都很舒適</figcaption></figure><p>當天實際測試錄音<br>效果相當滿意<br>成果可聽以下Podcast單集<br>後製僅作順剪和音量調整（響度正規化）</p><p>多人錄音容易出現串音狀況（別人的麥克風收到自己的聲音）<br>這是錄音空間建置的一大挑戰<br>就體驗當天的收音狀況來看<br>KKBOX STUDIO 整體空間的吸音、隔音處理很到位<br>些微串音直接混音也不會出現回音<br>基本上不影響收聽體驗</p><figure float=\"none\" data-type=\"figure\" class=\"img-center\" style=\"max-width: null;\"><img src=\"https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/8514f736-dee5-4f5f-a3eb-cd511a4d9190_800x450.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-node embed\"><figcaption HTMLAttributes=\"[object Object]\" class=\"\">原始檔麥克風串音狀況（選取範圍）</figcaption></figure><div class=\"relative header-and-anchor\"><h3 id=\"h-\">開幕活動</h3></div><div class=\"relative header-and-anchor\"><h4 id=\"h-\">官網預約</h4></div><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow ugc\" class=\"dont-break-out\" href=\"https://sp.kkbox.events/zh/KKBOX_STUDIO-630\">KKBOX STUDIO 官方網站</a></p><div class=\"relative header-and-anchor\"><h4 id=\"h-\">試營運優惠</h4></div><p>至2021/10/31試營運期間可輸入優惠碼「KKBOXSTUDIO」即享八折優惠！</p><div class=\"relative header-and-anchor\"><h4 id=\"h-\">加碼任務優惠</h4></div><p>曾經使用過錄音室並且使用KKBOX創作者後台獨家功能：音樂嵌入 和 AI 逐字稿，可額外獲得五折或六折折扣碼</p><div class=\"relative header-and-anchor\"><h3 id=\"h-\">延伸閱讀</h3></div><div class=\"relative header-and-anchor\"><h4 id=\"h-\">傑西大叔的<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow ugc\" class=\"dont-break-out\" href=\"https://blog.jesselin.com/index.php/2021/09/8018/\">開箱文</a></h4></div><p>講究的大叔針對空間和硬體設備配置、大樓出入口注意事項有超詳細圖文說明</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow ugc\" class=\"dont-break-out\" href=\"https://blog.jesselin.com/index.php/2021/09/8018/\"><strong>KKBOX STUDIO 寵壞PODCASTER的錄音室 - 這裡胡說 x 傑西大叔</strong><br><em>錄音設備使用RCP，每個房間都是四組PODMIC麥克風，也備有防噴網 每間錄音室都有WIFI AP，實際測試33上傳/87下載，如果要做影像直播會有點緊 交通地點上算方便，並且大樓下面有付費臨時停車位 50/HR 到晚上十點…</em>blog.jesselin.com</a></p><p>以上。</p><blockquote><p>Happy Podcasting!</p></blockquote><figure float=\"none\" data-type=\"figure\" class=\"img-center\" style=\"max-width: null;\"><img src=\"https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/fa1de81a-aae9-4084-b77a-4d4edacb6765_800x800.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-node embed\"><figcaption HTMLAttributes=\"[object Object]\" class=\"hide-figcaption\"></figcaption></figure><figure float=\"none\" data-type=\"figure\" class=\"img-center\" style=\"max-width: null;\"><p>歡迎每月小額贊助，支持我的Podcast創作、寫免費的podcast製作教學文章和推廣小鬱相關衛教活動</p><figcaption HTMLAttributes=\"[object Object]\" class=\"hide-figcaption\"></figcaption></figure>",
